{"tid":1258647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【All Eyes on Hong Kong】衝出國際之後，下一步想點做？","createTime":"2019-06-26T08:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T08:28:20.000Z","uid":263217,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"637ff693450f6f75c235bd448cf9c0453ee6bc83","tid":1258647,"uid":263217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"再次感謝各位巴打絲打守護香港，食催淚彈/遊行/唱詩/圍政總/警總/稅局/領事館/眾籌/登報/拍片/播片/假膠，乜都做齊，太令人滾動<br />\nJ完之後，回到現實，中環海濱割地直過，中共叫各國G20唔准討論香港。香港兒女秉承義士遺志，衝出國際賣廣告，要求國際社會#HelpHongKong，NY Times廣告列出三個訴求：<br />\n<br />\n1. To completely withdraw the Extradition Bill.<br />\n2. To release all the arrested unconditionally and undertake not to prosecute any of the protestors.<br />\n3. To appoint an independent commission of inquiry to look into incidents of police brutality.<br />\n<br />\n下一步要點做？發夢夢到下面D野<br />\n<br />\n1. 要求國際特赦組織譴責香港警方濫用暴力，並成立獨立調查團切查事件<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織確認香港警察違反國際人權法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1247785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1247785</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2. 要求英國政府外交干涉中共認真執行中英聯合聲明，還香港人真自治權，停止干預香港事務<br />\n<br />\n英國政府稱，有權介入香港事務，保護香港人基本自由，要求中共履行聯合聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1258065\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1258065</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n3. 要求美國通過新版人權民主法案，向中方施壓讓香港2020年真普選行政長官/立法會<br />\n<br />\n新版人權民主法案 美限港2020前普選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1253912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1253912</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n4. 靠自己，製作宣傳廣告，以現有動畫、警察濫權及蛇齋餅糭片段為藍本，力數港共/建制惡行，係YouTube落廣告<br />\n<br />\n[最新文宣片] We are Hongkongers! 同時原片德文、法文版本已經上線啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1257625\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1257625</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n5. 再搞大D，製作中共惡行影片合輯，推上HBO/ Netflix全球發行(不過套戲播一日都未播完)<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論，提供意見<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自修行<br />\n遍地開花，各有各做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c435abbbc397693e094882f9bf9ff2680952c836","tid":1258647,"uid":263217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:11:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8419ef20845e5d0f6f738a2fcfad1a0db30e11e2","tid":1258647,"uid":263217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008c20d3ddaade6d6a9b5bd195e685a290f7e445","tid":1258647,"uid":263217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd9a30a9e1fd9a01f8019ce30654e1349b249a23","tid":1258647,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:13:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQQREDk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQQREDk.png&h=190dd71d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2LmYZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2LmYZa.png&h=1855d90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前立法局主席黃宏發踢爆：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">議事規則得撤回 押後 postpone or withdraw</span><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇暫緩</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/PrrEBU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/PrrEBU</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">(懶既直接係最底copy) </span></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742c68d12418a39942b5387619314efb4703e102","tid":1258647,"uid":192068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:28:20.00